FeedPackage.Description:
A simple Singleton implementation of Log4Net Logger. Package will add required settings in web.config and add a folder Configuration at root, which will contain config for log4net. It also install Log4Net package.
Once installed, we can use it by :
CodeNode.Logging.Logger.Instance.Info("Message") CodeNode.Logging.Logger.Instance.Warning("Message") CodeNode.Logging.Logger.Instance.Error(ex); // ex => Exception CodeNode.Logging.Logger.Instance.Fatal(ex);// ex => Exception
It will create a Logs folder at root and will also create two log files. One for info and one for errors.
FeedPackage.ReleaseNotes: Added web transform file
